  Locus:
    Page: 221
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Habits
---
We stuff ourselves into little habitual ways of doing things ... and then
if we do not get to do it our way, or if someone comes along who wants to
do it differently, we get irritable and we become a nuisance to ourselves
and those around us.
